# SonarQube reports are generated here during CI pipeline runs
# Files generated:
# - shellcheck-report.txt  (shell script bugs & code smells)
# - yaml-analysis.log      (YAML file scan results)
# - security-findings.txt  (vulnerability scan)
# - code-smells.txt        (TODO/FIXME/HACK patterns)
# - duplication-report.txt (duplicate code)
# - quality-gate.log       (pass/fail verdict)
# - summary.txt            (full analysis summary)
